    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tears of the Maker is a roguelike deck builder. It requires a good use of card combinations and planning in order to defeat your enemies and take control of your fate.  </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tears flow to the chambers to determine who takes damage. Use the cards to manipulate various aspects of the game to gain the advantage. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249470/extras/6e5fdace3c2e2546c5f2d61bf3e4c2dc.avif?t=1761306683\" width=100 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Story Mode, collect powerful cards and grow your stats to save the land from a mysterious evil.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Endless Mode, no two runs are the same—only a well-forged deck can carry you through the unknown. You must build your deck in between each round as you earn money from defeating enemies. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249470/extras/5d2660d5a66b5cf83b7f2aaa7adb5e13.avif?t=1761306683\" width=100 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
